		<p>I certainly hope no one will be so rude as to mention Hodel's leadership of various conservative groups, such as the secretive Council of National Policy, of which he was president as recently as 2004.<br />
What is the CNP? <br />
Glad you asked. <br />
According to the New York Times, the CNP is â€œa few hundred of the most powerful conservatives in the countryâ€? who meet â€œbehind closed doors at undisclosed locationsâ€¦to strategize about how to turn the country to the right.â€?<br />
