Also some names you might not recognize, such as Foster Friess of Jackson Hole, Wyoming, who according to records maintained by <a href="http://www.newwest.net/?URL=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.opensecrets.org">http://www.opensecrets.org</a> is the top donor to conservative political campaigns in Wyoming.<br />
Hodel is a political creature of the far right and knows many of the key figures linked to the Abramoff scandal -- like Norquist and Ralph Reed.</p>
		
